                     <interp inst="t18260216-79-person645" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at a pawnbroker's in Cripplegate. The prisoner pawned these things with me on the 28th of January, about eleven o'clock at night.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I was in great distress.</p>
